Sentencas: Novel electrolyte materials for solid oxide fuel cells based on Sm-doped SrMo0.5W0.5O4 were synthesized by hydrothermal method.
Titulo: An investigation on novel electrolyte materials with scheelite structure for solid oxide fuel cells

Sentencas: Their phase composition, sinterability and electrical conductivity were studied.
Titulo: An investigation on novel electrolyte materials with scheelite structure for solid oxide fuel cells

Sentencas: Results show that the prepared powders have a pure scheelite structure at 500 degrees C with superior sinterability.
Titulo: An investigation on novel electrolyte materials with scheelite structure for solid oxide fuel cells

Sentencas: The electrical conductivity of the samples can significantly improved by doping with appropriate Sm2O3.
Titulo: An investigation on novel electrolyte materials with scheelite structure for solid oxide fuel cells

Sentencas: The maximal electrical conductivity of 0.058 S cm-1 at 800 degrees C can be observed in the Sr0.9Sm0.1Mo0.5W0.5O4 electrolyte ceramic sample.
Titulo: An investigation on novel electrolyte materials with scheelite structure for solid oxide fuel cells

Sentencas: Sr1-xSmxMo0.5W0.5O4 is suggested as a potential electrolyte for intermediate temperature solid oxide fuel cells due to its superior sinterability and electrical performance.
Titulo: An investigation on novel electrolyte materials with scheelite structure for solid oxide fuel cells
